Package ispd.motor.random

Record Class TwoStageUniform

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
ispd.motor.random.TwoStageUniform
public record TwoStageUniform(double minimum, double intervalSplit, double maximum, double firstIntervalProbability) extends Record
Utility class to contain information about computing or communication sizes. They are expressed as an inclusive range, with an interval split and probability for the first interval (parameters for a two-stage uniform distribution).
